So, now to install the DocBook DTDs:

<pre>cd /usr/local/share/docbook
sudo wget http://www.oasis-open.org/docbook/xml/4.2/docbook-xml-4.2.zip
sudo unzip docbook-xml-4.2.zip -d docbook-xml-4.2
sudo xmlcatalog --noout --add nextCatalog '' file:///usr/local/share/docbook/docbook-xml-4.2/catalog.xml --create /etc/xml/catalog</pre>

Now the xmlto install finally works:

<pre>cd path_to_xmlto
make clean
./configure
make
make check
sudo make install</pre>

